						<tr>
							<td valign="top" width="100%">
								<center>Read the article on <a href="http://week.manoramaonline.com/cgi-bin/MMONLine.dll/portal/ep/theWeekContent.do?programId=10350676&channelId=-1073908026&contentId=14010715&tabId=13BV_ID%3D%40%40%40#.UZJS8JZ1mvM.facebook" target="_blank">The Week</a> website<br>&nbsp;</center>
